exports[`QAComponent > renders answers 1`] = `
"<div data-v-bcc04aab="" class="flex-container flex-col">
  <h2 class="label-like">Common Questions</h2>
  <div data-v-bcc04aab="" data-state="open" data-orientation="vertical">
    <h3 data-v-bcc04aab="" data-orientation="vertical" data-state="open"><button data-v-ee781121="" data-v-bcc04aab="" class="button-like button button--primary w-full justify-between" type="button" aria-controls="reka-collapsible-content-v-1" aria-expanded="true" data-state="open" id="reka-accordion-trigger-v-0" data-reka-collection-item="" data-orientation="vertical" data-test-id="qa-button-appPurpose">
        <!--v-if-->What's this app for? <svg data-v-bcc04aab="" style="width: 1.25rem; height: 1.25rem;" class="shrink-0 rotate-180 transition duration-200" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M7.41,8.58L12,13.17L16.59,8.58L18,10L12,16L6,10L7.41,8.58Z" class="transition-all"></path>
        </svg>
      </button></h3>
    <div data-v-bcc04aab="" role="region" aria-labelledby="reka-accordion-trigger-v-0" data-state="open" data-orientation="vertical" style="--reka-accordion-content-width: var(--reka-collapsible-content-width); --reka-accordion-content-height: var(--reka-collapsible-content-height); --reka-collapsible-content-height: 0px; --reka-collapsible-content-width: 0px;" class="collapsible-content" data-test-id="qa-panel-appPurpose" id="reka-collapsible-content-v-1">
      <div data-v-bcc04aab="" class="whitespace-pre-line p-2">Eat Your Veggies is a free app for tracking plant-based ingredients in your diet. Whenever you eat plant-based ingredients, or "veggies", you can search them in the app and add them to your weekly record. Each veggie counts only once per week.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div data-v-bcc04aab="" data-state="open" data-orientation="vertical">
    <h3 data-v-bcc04aab="" data-orientation="vertical" data-state="open"><button data-v-ee781121="" data-v-bcc04aab="" class="button-like button button--primary w-full justify-between" type="button" aria-controls="reka-collapsible-content-v-3" aria-expanded="true" data-state="open" id="reka-accordion-trigger-v-2" data-reka-collection-item="" data-orientation="vertical" data-test-id="qa-button-howToInstall">
        <!--v-if-->How to install? <svg data-v-bcc04aab="" style="width: 1.25rem; height: 1.25rem;" class="shrink-0 rotate-180 transition duration-200" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M7.41,8.58L12,13.17L16.59,8.58L18,10L12,16L6,10L7.41,8.58Z" class="transition-all"></path>
        </svg>
      </button></h3>
    <div data-v-bcc04aab="" role="region" aria-labelledby="reka-accordion-trigger-v-2" data-state="open" data-orientation="vertical" style="--reka-accordion-content-width: var(--reka-collapsible-content-width); --reka-accordion-content-height: var(--reka-collapsible-content-height); --reka-collapsible-content-height: 0px; --reka-collapsible-content-width: 0px;" class="collapsible-content" data-test-id="qa-panel-howToInstall" id="reka-collapsible-content-v-3">
      <div data-v-bcc04aab="" class="whitespace-pre-line p-2">Android users can install our app from <a data-v-bcc04aab="" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=app.eatyourveggies.twa" class="text-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Play</a>.

        Others can install the app from a browser that supports Progressive Web Apps (PWAs). Select "Add to start screen" from your browser's menu or click the install icon on the location bar. On mobile Safari, click "Share" and then "Add to home screen". Installing on device allows offline use, but keeps the app within your browser's sandbox.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div data-v-bcc04aab="" data-state="open" data-orientation="vertical">
    <h3 data-v-bcc04aab="" data-orientation="vertical" data-state="open"><button data-v-ee781121="" data-v-bcc04aab="" class="button-like button button--primary w-full justify-between" type="button" aria-controls="reka-collapsible-content-v-5" aria-expanded="true" data-state="open" id="reka-accordion-trigger-v-4" data-reka-collection-item="" data-orientation="vertical" data-test-id="qa-button-studyDetails">
        <!--v-if-->What's the science? <svg data-v-bcc04aab="" style="width: 1.25rem; height: 1.25rem;" class="shrink-0 rotate-180 transition duration-200" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M7.41,8.58L12,13.17L16.59,8.58L18,10L12,16L6,10L7.41,8.58Z" class="transition-all"></path>
        </svg>
      </button></h3>
    <div data-v-bcc04aab="" role="region" aria-labelledby="reka-accordion-trigger-v-4" data-state="open" data-orientation="vertical" style="--reka-accordion-content-width: var(--reka-collapsible-content-width); --reka-accordion-content-height: var(--reka-collapsible-content-height); --reka-collapsible-content-height: 0px; --reka-collapsible-content-width: 0px;" class="collapsible-content" data-test-id="qa-panel-studyDetails" id="reka-collapsible-content-v-5">
      <div data-v-bcc04aab="" class="whitespace-pre-line p-2">According to a study, consuming 30 or more veggies weekly has multiple health benefits over a less versatile diet. The key, according to study, is not just the amounts you consume, but also variation. If you want to read more about the study, look up The American Gut Project from the journal of <a data-v-bcc04aab="" href="https://doi.org/10.1128/msystems.00031-18" class="text-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">American Society for Microbiology (ASM)</a>.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div data-v-bcc04aab="" data-state="open" data-orientation="vertical">
    <h3 data-v-bcc04aab="" data-orientation="vertical" data-state="open"><button data-v-ee781121="" data-v-bcc04aab="" class="button-like button button--primary w-full justify-between" type="button" aria-controls="reka-collapsible-content-v-7" aria-expanded="true" data-state="open" id="reka-accordion-trigger-v-6" data-reka-collection-item="" data-orientation="vertical" data-test-id="qa-button-whatCounts">
        <!--v-if-->What counts as a portion? <svg data-v-bcc04aab="" style="width: 1.25rem; height: 1.25rem;" class="shrink-0 rotate-180 transition duration-200" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M7.41,8.58L12,13.17L16.59,8.58L18,10L12,16L6,10L7.41,8.58Z" class="transition-all"></path>
        </svg>
      </button></h3>
    <div data-v-bcc04aab="" role="region" aria-labelledby="reka-accordion-trigger-v-6" data-state="open" data-orientation="vertical" style="--reka-accordion-content-width: var(--reka-collapsible-content-width); --reka-accordion-content-height: var(--reka-collapsible-content-height); --reka-collapsible-content-height: 0px; --reka-collapsible-content-width: 0px;" class="collapsible-content" data-test-id="qa-panel-whatCounts" id="reka-collapsible-content-v-7">
      <div data-v-bcc04aab="" class="whitespace-pre-line p-2">Ultimately, how you use the app is up to your discretion. However, consider that minuscule amounts might not be of any nutritional value. It is also worth noting that very processed foods don't count towards a portion. So ketchup should not equal a tomato.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div data-v-bcc04aab="" data-state="open" data-orientation="vertical">
    <h3 data-v-bcc04aab="" data-orientation="vertical" data-state="open"><button data-v-ee781121="" data-v-bcc04aab="" class="button-like button button--primary w-full justify-between" type="button" aria-controls="reka-collapsible-content-v-9" aria-expanded="true" data-state="open" id="reka-accordion-trigger-v-8" data-reka-collection-item="" data-orientation="vertical" data-test-id="qa-button-categories">
        <!--v-if-->But strawberry is a... <svg data-v-bcc04aab="" style="width: 1.25rem; height: 1.25rem;" class="shrink-0 rotate-180 transition duration-200" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M7.41,8.58L12,13.17L16.59,8.58L18,10L12,16L6,10L7.41,8.58Z" class="transition-all"></path>
        </svg>
      </button></h3>
    <div data-v-bcc04aab="" role="region" aria-labelledby="reka-accordion-trigger-v-8" data-state="open" data-orientation="vertical" style="--reka-accordion-content-width: var(--reka-collapsible-content-width); --reka-accordion-content-height: var(--reka-collapsible-content-height); --reka-collapsible-content-height: 0px; --reka-collapsible-content-width: 0px;" class="collapsible-content" data-test-id="qa-panel-categories" id="reka-collapsible-content-v-9">
      <div data-v-bcc04aab="" class="whitespace-pre-line p-2">...false fruit, I know. Also tomato is not a vegetable in biological sense, so the app takes some liberties in its categories. Still, please report any major inaccuracies you come across! You can also request missing veggies to be added. They should be such that are commercially available globally.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div data-v-bcc04aab="" data-state="open" data-orientation="vertical">
    <h3 data-v-bcc04aab="" data-orientation="vertical" data-state="open"><button data-v-ee781121="" data-v-bcc04aab="" class="button-like button button--primary w-full justify-between" type="button" aria-controls="reka-collapsible-content-v-11" aria-expanded="true" data-state="open" id="reka-accordion-trigger-v-10" data-reka-collection-item="" data-orientation="vertical" data-test-id="qa-button-isItFree">
        <!--v-if-->Is the app monetized? <svg data-v-bcc04aab="" style="width: 1.25rem; height: 1.25rem;" class="shrink-0 rotate-180 transition duration-200" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M7.41,8.58L12,13.17L16.59,8.58L18,10L12,16L6,10L7.41,8.58Z" class="transition-all"></path>
        </svg>
      </button></h3>
    <div data-v-bcc04aab="" role="region" aria-labelledby="reka-accordion-trigger-v-10" data-state="open" data-orientation="vertical" style="--reka-accordion-content-width: var(--reka-collapsible-content-width); --reka-accordion-content-height: var(--reka-collapsible-content-height); --reka-collapsible-content-height: 0px; --reka-collapsible-content-width: 0px;" class="collapsible-content" data-test-id="qa-panel-isItFree" id="reka-collapsible-content-v-11">
      <div data-v-bcc04aab="" class="whitespace-pre-line p-2">The app is free to use, and it has no advertisements. There will be a possibility to donate, but don't feel obliged.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div data-v-bcc04aab="" data-state="open" data-orientation="vertical">
    <h3 data-v-bcc04aab="" data-orientation="vertical" data-state="open"><button data-v-ee781121="" data-v-bcc04aab="" class="button-like button button--primary w-full justify-between" type="button" aria-controls="reka-collapsible-content-v-13" aria-expanded="true" data-state="open" id="reka-accordion-trigger-v-12" data-reka-collection-item="" data-orientation="vertical" data-test-id="qa-button-isMyDataSafe">
        <!--v-if-->Is my data safe? <svg data-v-bcc04aab="" style="width: 1.25rem; height: 1.25rem;" class="shrink-0 rotate-180 transition duration-200" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M7.41,8.58L12,13.17L16.59,8.58L18,10L12,16L6,10L7.41,8.58Z" class="transition-all"></path>
        </svg>
      </button></h3>
    <div data-v-bcc04aab="" role="region" aria-labelledby="reka-accordion-trigger-v-12" data-state="open" data-orientation="vertical" style="--reka-accordion-content-width: var(--reka-collapsible-content-width); --reka-accordion-content-height: var(--reka-collapsible-content-height); --reka-collapsible-content-height: 0px; --reka-collapsible-content-width: 0px;" class="collapsible-content" data-test-id="qa-panel-isMyDataSafe" id="reka-collapsible-content-v-13">
      <div data-v-bcc04aab="" class="whitespace-pre-line p-2">The data is stored in your browser's local storage and is not shared with any third parties. You can at any time you wish reset the app using the button below.</div>
    </div>
